{"tid":815504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3中國女遊客日本住民宿 遺下遍地垃圾M巾","createTime":"2018-09-12T06:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T08:31:41.000Z","uid":75969,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c6021a60034c12cad1ac53629f7914ec37317046","tid":815504,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T06:06:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180912/_2018091212321945732.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180912%2F_2018091212321945732.jpg&h=6ccc6390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">民宿主人發現3名女子退房後屋內一片凌亂及滿是垃圾。網圖</span><br />\n<br />\n一名在日本開民宿的中國老闆星期一(10日)發文稱，3名中國女遊客日前透過Airbnb入住他家民宿，離開時卻將遺下大量垃圾及用過的衛生巾，房間充滿惡臭異味，指根本就是搞破壞。事後，民宿老闆向Airbnb平台，並向3人索賠清潔費用。<br />\n<br />\n民宿的老闆都是中國人，他將相片放上微博，相片中可見，房間及廁所的地板上都堆了不少紙巾，用過的廁紙沒沖馬桶、廁紙丟在地上、還有用過的衞生巾、馬桶盖上還放了一張摺椅，以及飯廳的櫃上滿是東西及剩下的餐盤垃圾散落一地。<br />\n<br />\n老闆說，他在在日本開民宿已經有一年半時間，客人留下垃圾很正常，從來沒有遇到過這麼過分的客人，這3名女子的狀態根本是搞破壞，他事後透過Airbnb與這3名女子聯絡，要賠償6,666日圓清潔費（約470港元），還發生一些爭執。<br />\n<br />\n這3名女子看到微博發文後，其中1人還一度留言還擊：「我們是來住民宿，不是來收拾房子的！」。新聞傳出後，其後一名自稱姓岳女子向內地傳媒稱，曾在民宿老闆發佈的微博下方，解釋了為何會出現亂扔垃圾的行為，並願意向民宿老闆道歉並給予賠償。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，將椅子放置在馬桶上因廁所空間太小，為方便出入才將椅子放在馬桶上，因為走得才急忘記把椅子拿下來。又指民宿老闆將她們的信息曝光後，已引來眾多網友的口誅筆伐，甚至有網友人肉起底，她已經接到了很多騷擾電話，她試圖與民宿老闆協商解決但未成功。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180912/_2018091212294674458.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180912%2F_2018091212294674458.jpg&h=007e3cd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">飯廳的櫃上滿是東西及剩下的餐盤等垃圾。網圖<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180912/_2018091212294698853.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180912%2F_2018091212294698853.jpg&h=a40381d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">洗手間的馬桶上還架著一把椅子。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180912/_2018091212294498860.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180912%2F_2018091212294498860.jpg&h=735d0fba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">地板上都是紙巾垃圾。網圖<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180912/_2018091212294545118.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180912%2F_2018091212294545118.jpg&h=b061c760&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">留給客人使用的留言本，也被塗畫得亂七八糟。網圖<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/815476\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F815476&d=9N5G4lBSDNQ9%2FhAsjx6PY10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=8d9ddfe1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F815476&h=592fa04a\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/815476</a>"},{"pid":"981a4bd88e8d018ed817db1a591f2878097c31d0","tid":815504,"uid":75969,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T06:08:52.000Z","msg":"每次見到呢類新聞都以為係舊聞<br />\n睇清楚個日期先知強國客又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f993ae0ca5f01f2e2fd381b987d221387c04c2c","tid":815504,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T06:09:30.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗，不過酒店仲恐佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a205434c70bc3b14ff23604cec9f21fc461a8e89","tid":815504,"uid":38523,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T06:13:06.000Z","msg":"踩港五毛狗呢<br />\n準備好入來未？"},{"pid":"01400115dbb75e55cf86ddea